2023-01-05T02:50:38.449Z	babd0875-c920-4cd9-b931-4e2414d0b076	INFO	sql 
        SELECT l.couponId                                                                                      AS "クーポン交換ID",
               o.item.name.S                                                                                   AS "組織名",
               l.couponCode                                                                                    AS "クーポンコード",
               l.couponName                                                                                    AS "クーポン名",
               l.url                                                                                           AS "消し込みURL",
               l.barcode                                                                                       AS "バーコード番号",
               l.barcodeType                                                                                   AS "バーコードタイプ",
               CASE l.type
                   WHEN 'issued' THEN '発行済み'
                   WHEN 'used' THEN '使用済み'
                   ELSE 'キャンセル' END                                                                            AS "ステータス",
               date_format(from_unixtime(l.createAtMillis / 1000) AT TIME ZONE 'Asia/Tokyo', '%Y/%m/%d %H:%i') AS "日時",
               o2.item.name.S                                                                                  AS "利用店舗",
               l.terminalNumber                                                                                AS "端末コード",
               o2.item.customershopcode.S                                                                      AS "顧客店舗コード"
        FROM coupon_logs l
                 JOIN
             organization o
             ON o.item.resourceId.S = l.organizationId
                 LEFT JOIN
             organization o2 ON o2.item.resourceId.S = l.usedShopId
        WHERE l.type <> 'displayed'
            
AND l.couponMasterId = 'ee5ed107-db1e-41ce-b022-51037950b0f1'

AND NOT EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM coupon_logs AS l2
    WHERE l.couponId = l2.couponId
    AND l2.type <> 'displayed'    
    AND l.createAtMillis < l2.createAtMillis
)
AND l.couponMasterId = 'ee5ed107-db1e-41ce-b022-51037950b0f1'    






AND l.type IN ('','','used','')    
    
        ORDER BY
            l.couponName,
            l.barcode,
            l.createAtMillis,
            l.type,
            o.item.name.S
